main event: A UFO was reportedly sighted in Studio City, California on July 6, 1967.
interesting points: The report form indicates that the sighting was reported to the Air Force, but the information provided was not sufficient for a scientific evaluation.
The Air Force requested that the witness complete an FID Form 164 to provide more details about the sighting.
The report mentions that the witness and their friend saw the UFO, but no other details about the sighting are provided.
The report does not include any photographs of the UFO.
The conclusion on the report form states that the case has not been resolved and would be re-evaluated when more information is available.
